cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CY, cs.HC

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the evaluation of machine translation for informal, written bilingual dialogue. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves the use of neural MT systems. Additionally, it could be classified under cs.CY (Computers and Society) as it explores the analysis of MT-mediated communication and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction) as it involves the judgments of dialogue participants.
